patch

Oleg changed some code in MBSWizardHandler for bug 190155 where he processed the toolchains and add them to a List (see setCustomPagesFilter()).  Therefore he had to cast the toolchainList MBSCustomPageManager to List (see isPageVisible()).  But he didn't change the toolchains used in JUnit test TestCustomPageManager from a Set to a List.  I've updated this.  Please see my patch.  Thanks.
Patch applied to cdt_4_0 and HEAD.
